sets.summary: Get pumping for a rippling chest and your strongest arms ever.
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Intermediate week 7

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
It's time to get busy with a whole new set of moves for strong and rippling chest and arms.


Make sure you're nailing every exercise with the tutorial. Then when you're completing your reps comfortably and with good form, up your weight.


If you want to cool down after working out, you'll find the link to stretching sessions at the top of each week of workouts.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Switch on your chest and arms to take this workout all the way.

exercises.title: Barbell flat bench press (25% lifting weight)
Barbell flat bench press (50% lifting weight)

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Work your pecs and triceps on and off the bench.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: The incline shifts the benefits to your upper pecs, while your triceps work to stabilize both lifts.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Keep your form tight as the burn rises.
